snippet.title: Sum of the Interior Angles of a Triangle Proof | Paper Cutting Activity
snippet.description:
http://tapintoteenminds.com See why the interior angles of any triangle add up to 180 degrees through a paper cutting activity. 

This video introduces the geometric relationships learning goal in MPM1D: I can determine and describe the properties and relationships of the interior and exterior angles of triangles.
